        <div class="blog-content">
          <p class="lead">The web development landscape is constantly evolving, with new technologies, frameworks, and methodologies emerging regularly. In this comprehensive guide, we'll explore the most significant trends that are shaping the future of web development.</p>

          <h2 class="h3 mt-5 mb-3">The Rise of Component-Based Architecture</h2>
          <p>Modern web applications are increasingly built using component-based architectures. This approach promotes reusability, maintainability, and scalability by breaking down complex user interfaces into smaller, manageable pieces.</p>

          <div class="bg-light p-4 rounded my-4">
            <h4 class="h5 mb-3">Key Benefits:</h4>
