          <h2 class="h3 mt-5 mb-3">AI and Machine Learning Integration</h2>
          <p>Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning are becoming increasingly integrated into web applications, enabling features like personalized content, intelligent search, and automated optimization.</p>

